Package edu.escuelaing.arsw.ASE.app

Class MyLinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.escuelaing.arsw.ASE.app.MyLinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements stored in the linked list.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>
public class MyLinkedList<T> extends Object implements Iterable<T>
MyLinkedList represents a simple linked list data structure that stores elements of type T. It implements the Iterable interface to enable iteration over its elements.
